verse.lines:
If you need more joy, god's got it,
if you need more joy, god's got it,
if you need more joy, god's got it,
he's got it, and he's waiting to give it to you.

if you need more peace, God's got it,
if you need more peace, God's got it,
if you need more peace, God's got it,
He's got it, and He's waiting to give it to you.
